ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder Designating the Minister of Public Safety and Emergency Preparedness as the Minister for the Purposes of the Referendum Act
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2021-940 of October 26, 2021; and (2) designating the Minister of PUBLIC SAFETY AND EMERGENCY PREPAREDNESS, a member of the King’s Privy Council for Canada, as the Minister for the purposes of the REFERENDUM ACT.
